    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add a handful of <strong>flour</strong> to the <strong>sliced basa </strong>and give everything a good mix up until they are fully coated in the flour</p><p>Dip the <strong>floured</strong> <strong>basa</strong> in the <strong>batter</strong> (turn several times to coat completely)</p>",
